Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Costura, costura, costura, costura, costura, costura, costura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:55.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou juntá-los e tentar novamente!
