Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Costura, costura, costura, costura, costura, costura, costura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Costura, costura, costura, costura, costura, costura, costura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.96,Main,,0,0,0,,O que?!
