Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:04.95,Main,,0,0,1,,Señor, defenda a fábrica custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:06.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não! Desvie, Señor!{\i0}
